properties.TITLE: Greater Manchester AQMA
properties.DESCRIPTIO: A new single AQMA covering all 10 Local authorities in Greater Manchester. These are Manchester, Salford, Stockport, Tameside, Oldham, Bury, Bolton, Wigan, Rochdale and Trafford. The AQMA is declared on all areas exceeding the annual mean of 35ug/m3 incl
